    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Pencils that produce a permanent mark, non-erasable with any pencil eraser.The component materials of copying pencil cores are graphite, kaolin clay, and an aniline dye as colorant. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
